It doesn't mean he's afraid,

77
00:08:05,580 --> 00:08:11,075
- Doesn't it?
- Anyway, my father's here,

78
00:08:11,152 --> 00:08:15,350
Yours isn't coming back, is he?
Not ever,

79
00:08:15,423 --> 00:08:18,290
One day, You'll see,

80
