00:10:52,713 --> 00:10:54,647
How much you got there, boy?

118
00:10:57,284 --> 00:11:00,685
- It's yours,
- Thank you,

119
00:11:01,789 --> 00:11:05,156
You're welcome,,,
Mr, Nightshade, sir,

120
00:11:16,637 --> 00:11:18,628
('horn honks/dog barking.)

