Come on now, You know what they'll
do? They'll kill 'em,

148
00:13:04,712 --> 00:13:08,113
That's what they're gonna do,
Boy, I wish I was out there

149
00:13:08,182 --> 00:13:12,380
to run, to throw, tackle,,, touchdowns,
